The distribution game is changing‚Äîand @phoebegates saw it coming before most.

While others were still figuring out influencer marketing, she and the @phiaco team were already stacking strategies: influencer collabs for momentum, then pivoting hard into founder-led content for authentic connection.

Her takeaway from @garyvee hits different: when everyone has access to the same tech, your real competitive advantage is how you distribute. Not what you build‚Äîhow you reach people.

@foundr broke down the full playbook with her on their podcast.
